  "detailed_description": "<u>BURST WITCH</u> is a bullet hell game with the classic scrolling shooter gameplay.<br>Control different Witches to fight all kinds of enemies and enjoy the most exciting bullet hell experience with a wealth of ammo types and epic music!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Ⅰ】Customize Ammo Combination Freely</h2>Wider attack range, better penetration, homing bullets… a wealth of options to build your own ammo combination.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Ⅱ】Gothic Art Style</h2>Beautiful character portraits and 3D battle scenes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Ⅲ】Incredible Original Music</h2>Symphonic and jazz music delivers an immersive fighting experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001670/extras/bfd447c22822e1d69f1f2b4417146188.poster.avif?t=1768225576\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001670/extras/bfd447c22822e1d69f1f2b4417146188.webm?t=1768225576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001670/extras/bfd447c22822e1d69f1f2b4417146188.mp4?t=1768225576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001670/extras/08e61a24dbceae6b9a78a3d24e0ff23d.poster.avif?t=1768225576\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001670/extras/08e61a24dbceae6b9a78a3d24e0ff23d.webm?t=1768225576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001670/extras/08e61a24dbceae6b9a78a3d24e0ff23d.mp4?t=1768225576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<u>BURST WITCH</u> is a bullet hell game with the classic scrolling shooter gameplay.<br>Control different Witches to fight all kinds of enemies and enjoy the most exciting bullet hell experience with a wealth of ammo types and epic music!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Ⅰ】Customize Ammo Combination Freely</h2>Wider attack range, better penetration, homing bullets… a wealth of options to build your own ammo combination.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Ⅱ】Gothic Art Style</h2>Beautiful character portraits and 3D battle scenes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Ⅲ】Incredible Original Music</h2>Symphonic and jazz music delivers an immersive fighting experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001670/extras/bfd447c22822e1d69f1f2b4417146188.poster.avif?t=1768225576\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001670/extras/bfd447c22822e1d69f1f2b4417146188.webm?t=1768225576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001670/extras/bfd447c22822e1d69f1f2b4417146188.mp4?t=1768225576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001670/extras/08e61a24dbceae6b9a78a3d24e0ff23d.poster.avif?t=1768225576\" width=612 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001670/extras/08e61a24dbceae6b9a78a3d24e0ff23d.webm?t=1768225576\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2001670/extras/08e61a24dbceae6b9a78a3d24e0ff23d.mp4?t=1768225576\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
